attacks.name: Side Eye
attacks.effect: Switch 1 of your opponent’s Benched Pokémon with their Active Pokémon. The new Active Pokémon is now Confused.

attacks.name: Jumping Side Kick
attacks.effect: If your opponent’s Active Pokémon is Confused, this attack does 90 more damage.

attacks.name: Queen’s Command GX
attacks.effect: Your opponent discards 4 cards from their hand. (You can’t use more than 1 GX attack in a game.)
